OL,3,CYoung child in hospital and man
OL,4,Carrested after crossing crash
OL,6,FA young child is in hospital with
OL,7,Fserious injuries following a road
OL,8,Ftraffic collision in Wantage.
OL,10,FIt happened at around 6.25pm on
OL,11,FFriday, 12th June, when a black Ford
OL,12,FFiesta struck the youngster at the
OL,13,Ftraffic light crossing near The Health
OL,14,FCentre on Mably Way, Grove.
OL,16,FThey sustained serious injuries and
OL,17,Fremain in hospital at this current
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
