OL,3,CYoung child in hospital and man
OL,4,Carrested after crossing crash
OL,6,FA 37-year-old man from Wantage has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of causing
OL,8,Fserious injury by dangerous driving,
OL,9,Fdriving whilst unfit through drink/
OL,10,Fdrugs and driving otherwise than in
OL,11,Faccordance with a licence.
OL,13,FHe has been released on police bail
OL,14,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
