OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781453488
OL,3,CYoung child in hospital and man
OL,4,Carrested after crossing crash
OL,6,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,7,FSergeant Edward Crofts of the Serious
OL,8,FCollision Investigation Unit said:
OL,9,F"Any collision involving a young
OL,10,Fperson is particularly harrowing, but
OL,11,FI would like to thank those that came
OL,12,Fto the aid of victim and their family
OL,13,Fat the time of the collision.
OL,15,F"This included medical staff working
OL,16,Fnearby and members of the public who
OL,17,Fstopped to assist.
